            <h1 id="reset-account-help" class="item-center">How to Reset My Account Details</h1>
            <p class="item-center" style="font-size: 22px;">
                1)&nbsp;&nbsp;FIRST, from any page, click on the "Login" button, found in the bottom right corner of your screen. This can be found on the footer.
