                <br>See the red arrows, red box and red circle in the following image (click to enlarge):
            </p>
            <div class="col-1">
                <img class="image-center" src="assets/images/walkthroughs/4B-uploading-to-gallery.png" alt="Upload to the Gallery Step 3" style="height: auto; width: auto; max-width: 80%; cursor: pointer;" onclick="showImage('assets/images/walkthroughs/4B-uploading-to-gallery.png')">
