            <p class="item-center" style="font-size: 22px; padding-top: 40px;">
                2)&nbsp;&nbsp;NEXT, now that you have just logged in, you should already be on the home page, but you can make sure of this by clicking the "Home" menu button, on the left side of your screen at the top of the menu.
